name: TikzCivilEng
summary: Useful set of Tikz drawings for Civil Engineers
short_description:
This project aims to build a big set of Tikz Drawing, that are useful for the creation of Reports in Civil Engineering. 
The main topics are: Structural Analysis and Geomechanics at the moment, since those are the kind of drawing I need at the time (I am still studying).
